{"tid":527079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★劏房？新移民近58%住私樓?!","createTime":"2018-01-12T09:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T15:17:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18bc5cd1df32269f469d61c874ea40126c3d6b67","tid":527079,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"《2016年中期人口統計主題性報告：內地來港定居未足七年人士》<br />\n<br />\n新移民居住的房屋類型，在過去10年亦有顯著變動。在2006年，他們大比例居於公營租住房屋，佔多達52.4%，其次有37.3%住在私人永久性房屋；但至2016年，他們反而較多居於私人永久性房屋，佔57.7%，而居於公營租住房屋的只佔32.2%。<br />\n<br />\n2016年共117,523個家庭有至少一位成員為新移民，佔全港家庭4.7%。他們平均人數為3.3人，較全港家庭平均2.8人為高。80.5%的18歲及以上女性是與配偶及或子女同住，而男性的相應比例則是51.9%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180111/bkn-20180111170153360-0111_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180111%2Fbkn-20180111170153360-0111_00822_001.html&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=3f3b25d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180111/bkn-20180111170153360-0111_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"82621dc6eef6879219b8777f3474f67516824b8d","tid":527079,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2801b2ce25bbf68582029417939d9a78c501440e","tid":527079,"uid":87723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"水泉澳邨果D咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0b295f2c3ae0a4fe591d640be0cb0de96a886d","tid":527079,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B11201012016XXXXB0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB11201012016XXXXB0100.pdf&d=ZLlp%2BqdNaSGF4Tu9lAAn4R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=4d402c9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://ww